            "description": {
                "p": "You know the gust cantrip. Starting at 3rd level, you can cast the gust of wind spell once with this trait, and you regain the ability to cast it when you finish a long rest. Charisma is your spellcasting ability for these spells."
            },
            "sheet": [
                "You know the gust cantrip.",
                {
